---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Lukáš Kmoch | Software Engineer</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Portfolio of Lukáš Kmoch — .NET developer and tech enthusiast. Backend systems, fullstack applications, and AI-powered development." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Lukáš Kmoch | Software Engineer" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Portfolio of Lukáš Kmoch — .NET developer and tech enthusiast." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
